Parallel server - multiple clients, each in separate thread. Transfer file from client to server. Choose between TCP and UDP protocols.

REQUIRED:
  bindata gem

USAGE:
  $ ruby server.rb hostname port filename protocol
  $ ruby client.rb hostname port filename protocol
  
hostname - specifies hostname for server
port - specifies port for accept connections
filename - specifies file to send (recieve)
protocol - specifies protocol to work with

RUNNING:
  Try start server in one terminal window and start client in another.
  Type this:
  $ ruby server.rb 127.0.0.1 4455 ../output.pdf tcp
  # ruby client.rb 127.0.0.1 4455 ../input.pdf tcp
